These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, pineapple
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, dancing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy
1. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person eating pineapple##8
2. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
3. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | fanta      |
| Food          | pineapple | grapefruit    |
| Hobby         | dancing   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | comedy      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, teacher
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
3. the teacher is not to the right of the designer##8
4. the person driving the ship is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | milk        | coffee    |
| Hobby       | skydiving         | drawing |
| Job         | teacher | designer   |
| Transport   | ship               | jet-ski  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, musical
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, reggae
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, turkish
2 different pets are kept: lizard, snake
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the turkish is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime       | musical |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | reggae    |
| Nationality   | russian | turkish |
| Pet           | lizard        | snake   |

 #################################

 
