2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
5. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person eating cherry##8

